data.description: Long-range mountain and pastural views abound at this calendar-like east Tennessee property.  The 3BR/2.5BA home is situated on a level lot with a fully fenced in backyard.  Inside, new dark bamboo hardwood floors take you from foyer to great room.  The open-concept space features a living area with shiplapped accent wall and gas fireplace.  Flanked by the kitchen and living space, the dining area can accommodate a full-sized table and accent furniture.  And the kitchen. Wowza. Granite counters, loads of cabinetry, a center island and a large pantry are just a few of the highlights. The main level also hosts the lone half bath.  Upstairs, take notice of the laundry room, full bathroom and all three bedrooms.  The master suite features vaulted ceilings, double sink vanity, soaking tub and step-in shower. Come see it today!
